TextEng: I have no need of you. Die as you should!
I have questions I want answered.
Me not need yous. Die!
Me gots questions for you!
I want some information about these Old Ones.
Text: 그 '태고의 존재들'에 대해 정보가 좀 필요해.

TextEng: Me want info 'bout Old Ones.
Where can I find Desther?
Where Desther?
Go on. Just get out of here, coward.
You just run away now, worm.
I've decided to kill you after all.
Me kill you after all.
I've beaten you once. You'd better talk.
Text: 난 이미 한 번 널 이겼어. 입 여는 게 좋을 거다.

TextEng: You talk or me get mad! You no want me get mad!
Text: 말해! 안 그러면 나 화내! 나 화내는 거 너 싫지!

TextEng: Back to my initial questions now.
Okay, back to first questions.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> There's no harm in telling me now. You are through here.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 지금 말해도 상관없다. 넌 여기서 끝났다.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You done here. It no matter is you tell me now.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 너 여기서 끝났어. 지금 말해도 괜찮아.

TextEng: Either you start talking or I start removing your fingers!
Text: 말 안 하면 네 손가락부터 하나씩 잘라 버린다!

TextEng: You talk or me hack off you fingers!
Text: 말해, 아니면 너 손가락 잘라 버려!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You aren't holding anything back, are you?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You holding back on me, maybe?
You're holding out on me! Come clean or I'll burn your ears off!
Text: 날 속이려 드는군! 솔직히 말해, 안 그럼 네 귀를 태워 버리겠다!

TextEng: You know more! You tell or maybe me burn you good!
Text: 너 더 알고 있어! 말해, 아니면 내가 제대로 태워 버릴 거야!

TextEng: Who do you serve?
You know anything about any guards or traps nearby?
Text: 근처 경비나 함정에 대해 아는 게 있나?

TextEng: Who you serve?
You know about guards or traps around here?
Get out of my sight, coward.
Get lost, scared little worm!
I want to ask about Helm's Hold.
Me ask about Helm's Hold.
Why did you come here?! Why kill everyone?!
Text: 왜 여기 온 거야?! 왜 모두를 죽인 거지?!

TextEng: Why you do that? Why you come here and kill?!
Text: 왜 그런 거야? 왜 여기 와서 죽여?!

TextEng: I have to get moving. I wonder what to do with you.
Text: 난 가봐야 한다. 널 어쩌면 좋을지 고민이군.

TextEng: Me got to move on. What me do with you, hmm?
Text: 나 가야 해. 너를 어쩌면 좋지, 흠?

TextEng: Why was Neverwinter supposed to fall to plague?
Why Neverwinter gotta fall to this plague?
Text: 왜 네버윈터가 이 역병에 무너져야 해?

TextEng: Who promised you this? Where are they?
Text: 이걸 누가 약속했지? 그들은 어디 있지?

TextEng: Who tell you this stuff? Where you hear it?
Text: 이런 말 누가 했어? 어디서 들었어?
